'''和尚蟹屬'''（学名：{{lang|la|''Mictyris''}}）为[[和尚蟹科|和尚蟹科]]动物的一個屬。分布于[[日本|日本]]、[[中國大陸|中國大陸]]（[[广西|广西]]、[[广东|广东]]、[[福建|福建]]等地）、[[香港|香港]]、[[台灣|台灣]]、[[菲律宾|菲律宾]]、[[马来群岛|马来群岛]]、[[新加坡|新加坡]]及[[印尼|印尼]]部分地區（[[卡拉克隆島|卡拉克隆島]]、[[巴韋安島|巴韋安島]]及[[安汶岛|安汶岛]]）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://species-identification.org/species.php?species_group=crabs_of_japan&menuentry=soorten&id=1755 |title=''Mictyris brevidactylus'' |work=Crabs of Japan |publisher=Marine Species Identification Portal |accessdate=2010-01-16 |language=en |archive-date=2014-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222061135/http://species-identification.org/species.php?species_group=crabs_of_japan&menuentry=soorten&id=1755 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[新喀里多尼亚|新喀里多尼亚]]、[[塔斯马尼亚|塔斯马尼亚]]、[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]及[[印度洋|印度洋]]的[[尼科巴|尼科巴]]與[[安达曼|安达曼]]。

生活在[[潮间带|潮间带]]沙土的地道或河口的[[泥滩|泥滩]]上<ref name='id11923'>{{cite web| url =http://www.bioinfo.cn/db05/BjdwSpecies.php?action=view&id=11923| title =长腕和尚蟹| work =《中国动物物种编目数据库》| publisher =中国科学院微生物研究所| author =中国科学院动物研究所| accessdate =2009-04-28| language =zh-hans| deadurl =yes| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20131203122335/http://www.bioinfo.cn/db05/BjdwSpecies.php?action=view| archivedate =2013-12-03}}</ref>，退潮时出来活动。雌雄间没有明显差异，需将腹部打开才能分辨。平均体重约为2克，能够直立行走。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://edu.ocac.gov.tw/local/mangrove/e/ec/ec2a05.htm |title=''Mictyris brevidactylus'' |work=Exploring Taiwan Mangroves |publisher=[[中華民國僑務委員會|Overseas Compatriot Affairs Commission]] |accessdate=2010-01-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110927162116/http://edu.ocac.gov.tw/local/mangrove/e/ec/ec2a05.htm |archivedate=2011-09-27 }}</ref>

和尚蟹屬物種的可預測特性，使之用於製作{{link-en|桌球電腦|Billiard-ball_computer}}
<ref>{{cite web |author=Jacob Aron |date=2012-04-12 |title=Computers powered by swarms of crabs |publisher=[[New_Scientist|New Scientist]] |url=http://www.newscientist.com/blogs/onepercent/2012/04/researchers-build-crab-powered.html |accessdate=April 15, 2012 |archive-date=2017-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170803053008/https://www.newscientist.com/blogs/onepercent/2012/04/researchers-build-crab-powered.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Yukio-Pegio Gunji, Yuta Nishiyama & [[Andrew_Adamatzky|Andrew Adamatzky]]  |year=2011 |title=Robust soldier crab ball gate |journal=[[Complex_Systems_(journal)|Complex Systems]] |volume=20 |page=2 |arxiv=1204.1749}}</ref>。

